# Altitude Test Mission
# Description: Tests climb/descent performance at different altitudes
#
# Mission Profile:
# - Takeoff to 50m
# - Climb to 100m, 150m, 200m waypoints
# - Maintain 200m altitude
# - Descend through 150m, 100m, 50m
# - Land
#
# Expected Duration: ~10 minutes
# Max Altitude: 200m AGL
#
# Usage:
#   wp load altitude_test.waypoints
#   mode AUTO
#
# Good for:
# - TECS tuning (climb/sink rates)
# - Altitude hold testing
# - Airspeed control validation
#
# Watch parameters:
# - TECS_CLMB_MAX (max climb rate)
# - TECS_SINK_MAX (max sink rate)
# - TECS_TIME_CONST (response time)
#
# Author: Patrick Kelly (@Kuscko)
# Version: 1.0
